  "detailed_description": "<strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Old school metroidvania style game play with a similar level of old school difficulty.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 150 areas to explore and clear of enemies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Select from five unique special weapons to equip.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Collect gears and use them to upgrade and replenish your droids shield and ammo supply. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Great soundtrack.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Saves local high score stats and military ranks.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quit and restore game at any time without losing progress.</li></ul>",
